gov.usgs.volcanoes.winston.in.ew

Class ImportWSJob

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.usgs.volcanoes.winston.in.ew.ImportWSJob

  • public class ImportWSJob
extends Object
    If a span is added to the job it is an explicit guarantee that there is no existing data in that span. Therefore incoming TraceBufs only need to be between the given span to avoid overlappers.
    Author:
    Dan Cervelli
